expanded your culinary
horizons beyond Italian?

01:55.100 --> 01:56.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
ALESSANDRA
MASTRONARDI: Yes, I am.

01:56.966 --> 01:58.266 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
