when I'm in New York?

02:03.900 --> 02:05.166 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
AZIZ ANSARI: Indian food.

02:05.166 --> 02:05.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
ALESSANDRA MASTRONARDI:
No, nobody likes curry.

02:05.966 --> 02:07.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
AZIZ ANSARI: Racist.

02:07.433 --> 02:08.666 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
ALESSANDRA MASTRONARDI: I
said I don't like curry food.

02:08.666 --> 02:10.766 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
