flavors my people enjoy.

02:20.500 --> 02:24.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Sonia, I saw you
both actually smiling watching
or even listening to that.

02:24.766 --> 02:26.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Sonia, tell us why
you like that show.

02:26.833 --> 02:31.433 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SONIA SARAIYA, "Variety": You
know, "Master of None" is --
it's such a delicate little,

02:32.033 --> 02:33.266 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
beautiful show.

02:33.266 --> 02:36.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Its a half-hour, but
it's so cinematic.

02:36.833 --> 02:40.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
There is -- actually, the
second season references
Italian cinema a lot.

02:40.666 --> 02:45.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You know, it's Aziz Ansari more
or less playing himself, you
know, trying to understand his

02:46.600 --> 02:48.633 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
life and figure out the world.

02:48.633 --> 02:52.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And, you know, a big thing
that motivates him, as you
can sort of tell, that's kind

02:52.133 --> 02:56.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of a date that he is on in
that clip, and, you know,
figuring out his love life is a

02:56.233 --> 02:58.266 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
big part of it.

02:58.266 --> 03:01.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But at the end of the first
season, he decided he wanted
to go to Italy and learn how to

03:01.300 --> 03:05.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
make pasta because that
was something that he
wanted to do in his life.

03:05.233 --> 03:09.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
The second season is
about him broadening
his horizons even more.

03:09.066 --> 03:11.600 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It is like a lovely little
vacation, that show.

03:11.600 --> 03:15.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
