03:49.633 --> 03:52.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: Eric,
they are still doing it.

03:52.333 --> 03:53.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
They are still plotting.

03:53.333 --> 03:55.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It goes on and on.

03:55.166 --> 03:57.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
ERIC DEGGANS: Yes.

03:57.233 --> 04:00.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And, you know, I know
am so people have grown
tired of "House of Cards."

04:00.000 --> 04:03.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I think, if you are one
of those people, you are not
going to necessarily like the

04:03.400 --> 04:05.500 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
new season.

04:05.500 --> 04:08.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But the new season does have a
lot of political machinations
that I think are sort of the

04:08.566 --> 04:11.100 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
heart of the show's appeal.

04:11.100 --> 04:16.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And it also really deals with
the tension and the partnership
between these two very

04:18.033 --> 04:21.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
singular characters, Frank
Underwood by Kevin Spacey and
Claire Underwood played by Robin

04:21.933 --> 04:23.900 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Wright.

04:23.900 --> 04:26.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Let's look
ahead at some new programs that
you are looking forward to.

04:26.700 --> 04:28.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Sonia, start us
off, start us off.

04:28.500 --> 04:31.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
What are a couple of
things you really want
to let us know about?

04:31.033 --> 04:33.033 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
SONIA SARAIYA: Yes, absolutely.

04:33.033 --> 04:37.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Well, there is this crazy
little show called "Claws" on
TNT that is debuting next week,

04:37.866 --> 04:39.933 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
I think.

04:39.933 --> 04:44.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
