look at some of the real issues
that affect people in places

05:13.466 --> 05:15.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
that don't often make
it to your TV screen.

05:15.566 --> 05:17.633 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So, I'm really looking forward
to see how that goes too.

05:17.633 --> 05:21.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
ERIC DEGGANS: Well, you
mentioned at the start
of this segment "GLOW,"
the Netflix series

05:21.333 --> 05:25.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
about the -- well,
the gorgeous ladies of
wrestling is what I think.

05:25.866 --> 05:30.866 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It is about the start of
a female wrestling league.

05:32.766 --> 05:36.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And it is really the start about
these sort of lovable losers
and their attempts to sort

05:38.433 --> 05:42.833 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
